{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Annual increase should rise by the same amount for both Old & New State Pension",
        "additional_details": "Because inflation affects the cost of living equally, but each year the gap between both pensions can widen, which I think is unfair. Also, it can increase the amount of pensioners requiring extra benefits!",
        "background": "I would like the annual state pension increase to be the same amount for both the Old and New State Pension, based on the triple lock.",
